tomcat-server-manager (0.1.7~lucid) lucid; urgency=low

  * Fixed bug #12: Sudo Authentication failure
  * Fixed bug #11: Check if instance-user exists
  * Fixed bug #10: Command list-versions fails
  * Fixed bug #9: Instance directory layout is now explained in man page
  * Fixed bug #7: Starting instance gives shell warning
  * Fixed bug #5: start instance with empty parameter fails
  * Fixed bug #13: Services are not started at boot time
  * Feature: Ports are now allocated automatically
  * All the init.d commands are now working correctly

